A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Mr. Dexter Percil; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Mr. Dexter Percil is a people-centric leader with a magnetic personality and
3 sharp intellect who has left an indelible mark on prestigious commercial entities across the
4 Caribbean; and
5 WHEREAS, Mr. Percil's significant organizational and leadership talents, remarkable
6 patience and diplomacy, keen sense of vision, and sensitivity to the needs of his community
7 have earned him the respect and admiration of his colleagues and associates; and
8 WHEREAS, as the Commercial Manager at Blue Waters St. Lucia Ltd., Mr. Percil provided
9 strategic leadership and direction to the Commercial team, driving sales growth, marketing
10 strategies, and outbound logistic strategies; and
11 WHEREAS, under his leadership, the company achieved an outstanding $9 million sales
12 growth in just two years, surpassing budget expectations and achieving remarkable
13 year-over-year revenue growth; and
