14 WHEREAS, during his tenure as the Senior Sales & Marketing Manager for Wines, Spirits,
15 Tobacco & Brewery at Peter & Company Distribution Ltd., Mr. Percil conceptualized and
16 launched the marketing strategy for PCD Experiences, resulting in increased brand
17 engagement and experiential marketing exposure and leading to a significant boost in
18 departmental sales revenue from $40 million to $50 million in 2018, with a gross profit
19 exceeding $10 million; and
20 WHEREAS, as the Export Sales Manager at Banks Holding Ltd. in Barbados, Mr. Percil
21 executed a successful Pinehill visibility campaign across seven Caribbean markets, resulting
22 in an over 50 percent brand awareness increase; and
23 WHEREAS, his journey is a testament to his unwavering commitment to excellence, his
24 ability to forge strong connections, and his continuous pursuit of innovative solutions in the
25 ever-evolving landscape of business; and
26 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding achievements of this
27 exemplary business leader are appropriately recognized.
28 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
29 the members of this body recognize and commend Mr. Dexter Percil as a true inspiration in
30 the world of sales and marketing as well as extend their sincere best wishes for his continued
31 success.
32 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
33 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Mr.
34 Dexter Percil.
